<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Employment Offer & Next Steps</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
    table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
    img { -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border: 0; height: auto; line-height: 100%; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }
    body { height: 100% !important; margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; background-color: #f4f4f4; }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container { width: 100% !important; margin: auto !important; }
      .fluid { max-width: 100% !important; height: auto !important; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important; }
      .stack-column, .stack-column-center { display: block !important; width: 100% !important; max-width: 100% !important; direction: ltr !important; }
      .stack-column-center { text-align: center !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0 !important; padding:0 !important; background-color:#f4f4f4;">
  <div style="display:none; font-size:1px; line-height:1px; max-height:0; max-width:0; opacity:0; overflow:hidden; mso-hide:all; font-family:sans-serif;">
    Your employment offer and pre-employment steps from Qcare.
  </div>

  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="background-color:#f4f4f4;">
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" class="email-container" style="background-color:#ffffff;">
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding:20px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #dddddd;">
              <%= image_tag "qcare_logo.png", width: 150, alt: "Qcare Logo" %>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:40px 30px;">
              <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-family:sans-serif; font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:#333333;">
                    Your Employment Offer & Next Steps
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:20px 0 10px; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#555555;">
                    Hi <%= (@user.try(:first_name) || @user.try(:name) || @name || "there") %>,
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-family:sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#555555;">
                    I would like to take this opportunity to inform you that your application for employment has been successful pending successful completion of the pre‑employment checks.
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:20px 0 0; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#555555;">
                    You will need to create an online employee file. To create your new employee file please launch your web browser and go here:
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding:16px 0 8px;">
                    <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="border-radius:25px; background-color:#9963f1ff;">
                            <%= link_to 'Create employee file', @onboarding_url %>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:24px 0 8px; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; color:#333333;">
                    Documents Attached
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-family:sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:24px; color:#555555;">
                    <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:18px;">
                      <li><strong>Letter of Offer</strong>: Contains pay rate info and an acceptance of employment page that needs to be printed and returned. <em>Print and sign page 4</em> and return by replying to this email with a photo, or message <a href="tel:0448129224" style="color:#6366f1; text-decoration:none;">0448&nbsp;129&nbsp;224</a>.</li>
                      <li><strong>Position Description and Code of Conduct</strong>: Details the requirements of your position.</li>
                      <li><strong>Fair Work Information Statement</strong>: Outlines employee entitlements in Australia, including casual employment info.</li>
                      <li><strong>ID Information Sheet</strong>: Lists the two forms of ID to add to your employee file.</li>
                    </ul>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:24px 0 8px; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; color:#333333;">
                    Pre‑Employment Checks (please complete)
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-family:sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:24px; color:#555555;">
                    <ol style="margin:0; padding-left:18px;">
                      <li>NDIS worker orientation module: <a href="https://training.ndiscommission.gov.au" target="_blank" style="color:#6366f1;">training.ndiscommission.gov.au</a>. Email completion certificate to <a href="mailto:ak@qcare.life" style="color:#6366f1;">ak@qcare.life</a>.</li>
                      <li>Two forms of ID emailed to <a href="mailto:ak@qcare.life" style="color:#6366f1;">ak@qcare.life</a>.</li>
                      <li>Create your employee file: <a href="https://podio.com/webforms/23975107/1738200" target="_blank" style="color:#6366f1;">Podio form</a>.</li>
                      <li>Acceptance of Letter of Offer: sign and email to <a href="mailto:ak@qcare.life" style="color:#6366f1;">ak@qcare.life</a>.</li>
                      <li>Create account & complete Qcare Support Worker Induction: <a href="https://link.edapp.com/V7Nj9aqVYlb" target="_blank" style="color:#6366f1;">EdApp link</a>.</li>
                      <li>Create roster profile for Deputy scheduling app: <a href="https://dpty.me/u/1lSVWSpbA6j8m0cQfAUHPLOFNVZ" target="_blank" style="color:#6366f1;">Deputy profile</a>.</li>
                      <li>Apply for NDIS screening check: <a href="https://workerscreening.dsdsatsip.qld.gov.au/workers/you-start" target="_blank" style="color:#6366f1;">Queensland worker screening</a>. Qcare company ID: <strong>4-G24F75I</strong>. If already obtained, please email a photo of your card to <a href="mailto:ak@qcare.life" style="color:#6366f1;">ak@qcare.life</a>.</li>
                    </ol>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td style="padding-top:24px; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#555555;">
                    If you have any questions at all, please do not hesitate to contact me.
                  </td>
                </tr>

              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding:20px 30px; background-color:#f4f4f4;">
              <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="font-family:sans-serif; font-size:12px; line-height:18px; color:#888888;">
                    <p style="margin:0;">Qcare QLD Pty Ltd</p>
                    <p style="margin:0;">PO Box 5553, Red Hill, QLD 4701, Australia</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding-top:10px; font-family:sans-serif; font-size:12px; line-height:18px; color:#888888;">
                    You are receiving this email because you have an employment application with Qcare.
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>